76561197969363150,Recommended,252690,18881392,"Posted: 4 November, 2015",all,Nullspeak,"This is a great piece of software. I run an ongoing game using FG and GoToMeeting, and while there is a learning curve and I had some initial difficulting opening a port to speak to the FG servers, it is more than worth it. Most of my players had never truly engaged with tabletop, and I myself had never run D&D 5th edition. But FG has made enough of the math automatic so as to be both newbie-friendly and to allow us to focus on the story, and on the weight of individual decisions, rather than mental sim-grind. Highly recommended."
